{"id": "wme1665702641178", "title": "Tab Position (TabPos)", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "Development Object and Property Reference", "Development Object Properties", "Presentation Properties", "FRM Widget Properties for Fields", "Tab Position (TabPos)"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wme1665702641178.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Tab Position (TabPos)</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:   Tab Orientation ( TabOrientation) \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:   Tab Orientation ( TabOrientation) \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fqh1665702641252.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:   Tabs Alignment (TabsAlignment) \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:   Tabs Alignment (TabsAlignment) \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wda1665702641324.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/wme1665702641178.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/wme1665702641178.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/wme1665702641178.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3616753\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3616753\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wme1665702641178.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wme1665702641178.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wme1665702641178.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wme1665702641178\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Position</span> widget property determines where the tab strip is located. By default, it is <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Top</code>.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wme1665702641178__p_d107939e1_d107940e1_d107941e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>TabPos<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Top</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">Bottom</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">Left</code> |\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">Right</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"wme1665702641178__table_d12716e1_d12717e1_d12718e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wme1665702641178__table_d12716e1_d12717e1_d12718e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wme1665702641178__table_d12716e1_d12717e1_d12718e1__entry__2\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wme1665702641178__table_d12716e1_d12717e1_d12718e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Top</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wme1665702641178__table_d12716e1_d12717e1_d12718e1__entry__2\">Displays tabs at the top of the widget </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wme1665702641178__table_d12716e1_d12717e1_d12718e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Bottom</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wme1665702641178__table_d12716e1_d12717e1_d12718e1__entry__2\">Displays tabs at the bottom of the widget. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wme1665702641178__table_d12716e1_d12717e1_d12718e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Left</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wme1665702641178__table_d12716e1_d12717e1_d12718e1__entry__2\">Displays tabs at the left side; not supported by\n                     TabEx widget </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wme1665702641178__table_d12716e1_d12717e1_d12718e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Right</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wme1665702641178__table_d12716e1_d12717e1_d12718e1__entry__2\">Displays tabs at the right side; not supported by\n                     TabEx widget </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wme1665702641178__section_h1q_w22_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d736288e145\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"wme1665702641178__table_d12719e1_d12720e1_d12721e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes for TabEx, No for Tab </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wme1665702641178__section_t3z_x22_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d736288e190\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wme1665702641178__p_d107948e1_d107949e1_d107950e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Position</span> property is\n            available on both the basic Tab and the extended TabEx widget, but the behavior\n            differs:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"wme1665702641178__ul_kmq_y22_1xb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wme1665702641178__li_d42272e1_d42273e1_d42274e1\">On the Tab widget, Windows desktop systems have\n               limited support for the <code class=\"ph codeph\">bottom</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">left</code>, and\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">right</code>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wme1665702641178__li_d42275e1_d42276e1_d42277e1\">On the TabEx widget, both the\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">top</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">bottom</code> values are fully supported on\n               desktop systems, but the <code class=\"ph codeph\">right</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">left</code> values are\n               not. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wme1665702641178__section_e5v_y22_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d736288e232\">Windows Desktop Limitations</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wme1665702641178__p_d107954e1_d107955e1_d107956e1\">Windows desktop systems have limited support for\n            tabs that are positioned at the bottom, or to the right or left, especially when themes\n            are used. In this case, the Uniface tabs are displayed using the specified theme and in\n            the correct position, but the following limitations apply:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"wme1665702641178__ul_w1p_cf2_1xb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wme1665702641178__li_d42278e1_d42279e1_d42280e1\">For the Tab widget, if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab\n                  Position</span> is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">Bottom</code>, the active tab has a line\n               at the top of the tab, instead of being seamlessly joined to the content. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wme1665702641178__li_d42281e1_d42282e1_d42283e1\">If <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Position</span> is set to\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">Left</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Right</code>: <ul class=\"ul\" id=\"wme1665702641178__ul_y1p_cf2_1xb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wme1665702641178__li_d42284e1_d42285e1_d42286e1\">When the mouse cursor is positioned over an\n                     inactive tab, the tab color does not change. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wme1665702641178__li_d42287e1_d42288e1_d42289e1\">Scroll buttons are not supported. </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wme1665702641178__p_d107957e1_d107958e1_d107959e1\">These are Windows-related issues that Uniface has\n            no control over.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wme1665702641178__section_z5h_df2_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d736288e278\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wme1665702641178__p_d107963e1_d107964e1_d107965e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zie1665702558978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of a field.\">$properties</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1705998763272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.\">$fieldproperties</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"wme1665702641178__pre_q5m_2f2_1xb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"TabPs=bottom\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wme1665702641178__section_xqt_2f2_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d736288e310\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"wme1665702641178__ul_bwx_ff2_1xb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wme1665702641178__li_d42290e1_d42291e1_d42292e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bzj1665702641924.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzj1665702641924.html\" title=\"The utab widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tab, which is mapped to utab.\">utab (Tab)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wme1665702641178__li_d42293e1_d42294e1_d42295e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616753\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616753\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Tab Position (TabPos) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The Tab Position widget property determines where the tab strip is located. By default, it is Top . \" TabPos = Top | Bottom | Left | Right \" Value Description Top Displays tabs at the top of the widget Bottom Displays tabs at the bottom of the widget. Left Displays tabs at the left side; not supported by TabEx widget Right Displays tabs at the right side; not supported by TabEx widget Usage Dynamic? Yes for TabEx, No for Tab Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Description The Tab Position property is available on both the basic Tab and the extended TabEx widget, but the behavior differs: On the Tab widget, Windows desktop systems have limited support for the bottom , left , and right . On the TabEx widget, both the top and bottom values are fully supported on desktop systems, but the right and left values are not. Windows Desktop Limitations Windows desktop systems have limited support for tabs that are positioned at the bottom, or to the right or left, especially when themes are used. In this case, the Uniface tabs are displayed using the specified theme and in the correct position, but the following limitations apply: For the Tab widget, if Tab Position is set to Bottom , the active tab has a line at the top of the tab, instead of being seamlessly joined to the content. If Tab Position is set to Left or Right : When the mouse cursor is positioned over an inactive tab, the tab color does not change. Scroll buttons are not supported. These are Windows-related issues that Uniface has no control over. Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see $properties and $fieldproperties . $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"TabPs=bottom\" Copy Applies to utab (Tab) utabex (TabEx) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}